::Prowl::

Prowl looks at Iron Raptor as she steps back, seeing her sneeze, and 
looking at her back in surprize as he sees the wings sprout out, 
watching them stretch to about 24 feet wingspan. He brings one of his 
own wings forward, looking at it and comparing it to Iron Raptor's. 
Her wins were a foot or two longer each.

Prowl can't help but let his eyes slide down her body as the wind 
blows her hair up, looking over her curves and smiling slightly, 
looking back up to her wings, his eyes pausing at several key places.

"Hmmm.... Now you're a full fledged angel, love..." he says in 
admiration.
